## Clases de superficie

### Card glass

```html
<div class="bg-glass backdrop-blur-glass border border-glass-border rounded-2xl p-6">
```

### Panel elevado (dropdown, tooltip)

```html
<div class="bg-surface-raised backdrop-blur-modal border border-glass-border rounded-xl p-4 shadow-xl shadow-black/40">
```

### Modal / Drawer

```html
<!-- Overlay -->
<div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-40" />

<!-- Panel -->
<div class="fixed inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-50 p-4">
  <div class="bg-surface-modal backdrop-blur-modal border border-glass-border
              rounded-3xl w-full max-w-lg p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-black/50">
```

