## Componentes base

### `BaseButton.vue` — tres variantes

```html
<!-- Primary -->
<button class="bg-brand hover:bg-brand-light text-white font-medium
               px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95">

<!-- Ghost -->
<button class="bg-transparent hover:bg-glass-hover border border-glass-border
               hover:border-white/20 text-white/80 hover:text-white
               px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200">

<!-- Destructive -->
<button class="bg-red-500/20 hover:bg-red-500/30 border border-red-500/30
               text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl
               transition-all duration-200">
```

### `BaseInput.vue`

```html
<div>
  <label class="text-xs font-medium text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2 block">
    {{ label }}
  </label>
  <input class="w-full bg-glass backdrop-blur-sm border border-glass-border rounded-xl
                px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-white/30
                focus:outline-none focus:border-brand/60 focus:bg-glass-hover
                transition-all duration-200" />
  <p v-if="error" class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1">{{ error }}</p>
</div>
```

### `BaseModal.vue`

```vue
<template>
  <Teleport to="body">
    <Transition name="modal">
      <div v-if="modelValue" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm" @click="$emit('update:modelValue', false)" />
        <div class="relative bg-surface-modal backdrop-blur-modal border border-glass-border
                    rounded-3xl w-full max-w-lg p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 z-50">
          <slot />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Transition>
  </Teleport>
</template>
```

### `GlassCard.vue`

```vue
<template>
  <div class="bg-glass backdrop-blur-glass border border-glass-border rounded-2xl" :class="padding">
    <slot />
  </div>
</template>

<script setup>
defineProps({ padding: { type: String, default: 'p-6' } })
</script>
```

