## Tipografía

```js
// tailwind.config.js
fontFamily: {
  sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
  mono: ['JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', 'monospace'],
}
```

| Uso | Tailwind |
|---|---|
| Heading grande | `text-2xl font-bold text-white` |
| Heading sección | `text-lg font-semibold text-white` |
| Body | `text-sm text-white/80` |
| Secundario | `text-sm text-white/50` |
| Label input | `text-xs font-medium text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wide` |
| Código | `text-sm font-mono text-brand-light` |

---

## Interacción y movimiento

```css
/* Transición estándar — hover, focus */
transition-all duration-200

/* Transición de layout — panels, drawers */
transition-all duration-300

/* Feedback táctil */
active:scale-95

/* Hover en filas de lista */
hover:bg-glass-hover rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 cursor-pointer px-3 py-2
```

Animaciones de entrada para modals/drawers via `<Transition>`:
```css
.modal-enter-from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); }
.modal-enter-active { transition: all 0.2s ease-out; }
.modal-leave-to { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); }
.modal-leave-active { transition: all 0.15s ease-in; }
```

---

## Z-index

| Capa | z | Uso |
|---|---|---|
| Base | 0 | Contenido |
| Sticky | 10 | TopBar |
| Dropdown | 20 | Menús |
| Drawer | 30 | Side panels |
| Overlay | 40 | Fondos oscuros |
| Modal | 50 | Paneles modales |
| Toast | 60 | Notificaciones |

